description: Ronnie's Italian Ice serves a frozen delicacy that’s silky smooth, creamy and delicious…you’ll swear its ice cream! Our Italian Ices are made from sophisticated ice cream machines that were imported directly from Italy along with using only the finest ingredients and a 100 year old secret recipe to give our customers over 150 unique flavors of the smoothest creamiest Italian ice available anywhere. It’s a tasty treat that everyone loves to enjoy!
name: Ronnie's Italian Ice
